room_title: Escape room "Dying Love" by Epic Escape Rooms in Valdosta
room_description:
Really? He chooses today to be neighborly and drop by for a visit? When you have friends and family over for a cookout?
Your neighbors have always been nice enough... but lately, he seems withdrawn and almost, well, crazy. Lurking behind pulled curtains, and only coming out to check mail and take his trash to the road after dark.
And she hasn't been seen for a couple of months now... You wonder to yourself if she has taken ill or something and you vow to be a better neighbor - to go by and check on her this week. But for today, you decide you had better get back to your guests and figure out why he came.
